channel.title: Eudora-World Help
channel.description:
Well, i'm sure you all know what "Eudora World 2.0" is. :D...
I need the codes/files for the Investment feature, cause i want that on a better server. But i have no clue on how to get alll the codes. :x...
Someone wanna help? :D
EDIT: How to i change Home? (like.. when you log in for the first time, how do i change it?)

item.title: Eudora-World Help
item.dc:creator: @Preist Preist
item.description:
@Preist wrote:

[quote=“Dastan_, post:2, topic:364748”][quote author=Preist link=topic=460952.msg3372101#msg3372101 date=1287319016]
EDIT: How to i change Home? (like… when you log in for the first time, how do i change it?)
[/quote]

Go to client.java/player.java and search for the current coords and change them.[/quote]

Mmk, Thanks a lot.
